<codeline><highlight class="normal">|<sp/>`scene/`<sp/>|<sp/>Scene<sp/>graph<sp/>integration<sp/>|</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">|<sp/>`rendering/`<sp/>|<sp/>Renderable<sp/>and<sp/>model<sp/>components<sp/>|</highlight></codeline>
